        ## Additional functionality
        The following external scripts can be used with HTML/CSS variants of Table to provide functionality that is already built into the web component version:

        ### Fixed column
        `fixed-column`: provides the functionality to create a fixed first or last column.

        To include this script, add the following to your application:
    {% endfilter %}

